column1: I prefer working alone rather than a larger group
I  focus on details rather than the bigger picture
I usually make decisions with logic instead of emotion

I get stressed really easily

I prefer to keep my options open
I can easily recognize patterns
I like to focus on one task at a time
I regularly make new friends
Seeing other people cry makes me want to cry too
I tend to stay calm even in extremely stressful situations
I usually finish one project before starting another
I am sentimental
I like to have to do lists
I usually apply common sense to problems
I would consider myself to be spontaneous
I believe that I'm more sensitive than others
I prefer to focus on possibilites than what's realistic
I spend a lot of time exploring random topics
I tend to think of the worst case scenario
I almost always have a backup plan
I consistently use schedules and lists

I get socially anxious when at a large party
I value justice and fairness over harmony and forgiveness
I usually describe things in a specific literal way
I would rather observe than be the center of attention
I enjoy ideas for their own sake rather than their actual use
I like to describe things figuratively
